{
  "nbformat": 4,
  "nbformat_minor": 5,
  "metadata": {
    "kernelspec": {
      "name": "maxima",
      "display_name": "Maxima",
      "language": "maxima"
    },
    "aximar": {}
  },
  "cells": [
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "# Numerical ODE Integration\n\nSolve ordinary differential equations with `np_odeint`, which wraps Fortran ODEPACK/DLSODE. Supports non-stiff (Adams) and stiff (BDF) methods.\n\nTwo calling conventions:\n\n- **Expression mode** — write the ODE symbolically: `np_odeint([f1, f2, ...], [t, y1, y2, ...], y0, tspan)`\n- **Function mode** — pass a callback: `np_odeint(f, y0, tspan)` where `f(t, y)` takes scalar `t` and ndarray `y`",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "load(\"numerics\")$\nload(\"numerics-integrate\")$\nload(\"ax-plots\")$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 15,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 1. Exponential Decay\n\nThe simplest ODE: $\\dot{y} = -y$, $y(0) = 1$. Exact solution $y(t) = e^{-t}$.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "tspan : np_linspace(0.0, 5.0, 50)$\nresult : np_odeint([-y], [t, y], [1.0], tspan)$\n\n/* Extract columns and compare with exact solution */\nt_col : np_slice(result, all, 0)$\ny_col : np_slice(result, all, 1)$\ny_exact : np_exp(np_scale(-1.0, t_col))$\nmax_err : np_max(np_abs(np_sub(y_col, y_exact)))$\nprint(\"Max error vs exp(-t):\", max_err)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 16,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Max error vs exp(-t): 1.1436221038912953e-7"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "ax_draw2d(\n  color=\"blue\", line_width=2, name=\"np_odeint\",\n  lines(np_to_list(t_col), np_to_list(y_col)),\n  color=\"red\", dash=\"dash\", name=\"exp(-t)\",\n  explicit(exp(-t), t, 0, 5),\n  title=\"Exponential Decay\", xlabel=\"t\", ylabel=\"y\",\n  grid=true, showlegend=true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 17,
      "outputs": [
        {
