    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 2. Harmonic Oscillator\n\nA 2D system: $\\dot{x} = v$, $\\dot{v} = -x$, with $(x_0, v_0) = (1, 0)$.\nExact solution: $x(t) = \\cos t$, $v(t) = -\\sin t$.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "tspan2 : np_linspace(0.0, float(4*%pi), 200)$\nres2 : np_odeint([v, -x], [t, x, v], [1.0, 0.0], tspan2)$\n\nt2 : np_slice(res2, all, 0)$\nx2 : np_slice(res2, all, 1)$\nv2 : np_slice(res2, all, 2)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 18,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "ax_draw2d(\n  color=\"blue\", line_width=2, name=\"x(t) = cos t\",\n  lines(np_to_list(t2), np_to_list(x2)),\n  color=\"orange\", line_width=2, name=\"v(t) = -sin t\",\n  lines(np_to_list(t2), np_to_list(v2)),\n  title=\"Harmonic Oscillator\", xlabel=\"t\", ylabel=\"\",\n  grid=true, showlegend=true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
